snippet.title: EmyLiveShow: S&M Story - release trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the depths of your fetishes with EmyLiveShow stars Emy and Nia! Spend amazing hours in the company of beautiful v-tubers and find out their secrets!

EmyLiveShow: S&M story is an adult visual novel with the mechanics of raising levels and the item system that open up new possibilities in the plot development.

Available now for PC and Android!
